You are a chemist. Now you are given a product molecule. Please predict the the reactant molecules of the reaction.
The reaction equation has the following format:
```
reactant1.reactant2. ... .reactantN>>product
```
Your task is to predict the structure representation of the reactant molecule. We provide the SMILES of the reactants.
